---
// Facilities — Lab equipment and testbeds
---

<section class="section facilities-section" id="facilities">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label animate-on-scroll">Facilities</div>
      <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">Where We Build</h2>
      <p class="section-desc animate-on-scroll">
        Our lab is equipped with industrial and research-grade platforms for real-world experimentation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="facilities-grid">
      <div class="facility-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="facility-icon">🦾</div>
        <h3>Manipulation Lab</h3>
        <p>Franka Panda arms, Allegro & Shadow Dexterous hands, force-torque sensors, and tactile skin arrays forfine manipulation research.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="facility-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="facility-icon">🏗️</div>
        <h3>Motion Arena</h3>
        <p>200㎡ tracked space with Vicon motion capture, configurable obstacles, and rough terrain patches for locomotion and navigation experiments.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="facility-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="facility-icon">🖥️</div>
        <h3>Compute Cluster</h3>
        <p>On-premise GPU cluster (8× A100) for large-scale simulation, policy training, and foundation model fine-tuning. Isaac Sim & MuJoCo ready.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="facility-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="facility-icon">🤖</div>
        <h3>Robot Fleet</h3>
        <p>Unitree Go2 quadrupeds, custom mobile manipulators, and DJI drone platforms for multi-agent field experiments.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="facility-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="facility-icon">📷</div>
        <h3>Perception Studio</h3>
        <p>Calibrated multi-camera rigs, LiDAR arrays, event cameras, and depth sensors for vision and multimodal perception research.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="facility-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="facility-icon">🏭</div>
        <h3>Industry TestBed</h3>
        <p>Partner factory floor access for real-world deployment testing — assembly lines, warehouse logistics, and inspection scenarios.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .facilities-section {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-header .section-label {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .section-header .section-label::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .facilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .facility-card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .facility-icon {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .facility-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .facility-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .facilities-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .facilities-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
